  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://purl.org/memo#TransformationDimension">
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">The primary dimension along which a VariantInstance transforms the source template (e.g. textual, visual, contextual). Enables typological analysis of meme variation.</rdfs:comment>
